{#Variables:#}
{#- user_name: full name of the user (publisher or information owner)#}
{#- entity_unpublish_date: unpublish date formatted with the tieto_date#}
{#- pages: array of pages#}
{#    - page: \Drupal\tieto_lifecycle_management_notifications\Data\EntityLifeCycleData object #}
{#- contact_mail: email address#}
<div>
    <p>Hello <span>{{ user_name }},</span></p>

    <p>The page you have published or where you are marked as an information owner is near to its expiration date.
        Please review the page, and either update and publish it again or withdraw it.
        Otherwise the page will be automatically unpublished on <span>{{ entity_unpublish_date }}</span>.</p>

    <p>Follow the link(s) to review the pages:</p>
    <ul>
        {% for page in pages %}
            <li><a href="{{ page.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">{{ page.title }}</a></li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>

    <p>Kind regards,</p>
    <p>Your Intra administrator</p>

    <p>In case you have questions related to this email youâ€™re welcome to contact <a href="mailto:{{ contact_mail }}">{{ contact_mail }}</a></p>
</div>
